'''優-{}-步'''（{{lang-en|-{Uber}-}}，{{IPAc-en|'|u:|b|@|r}}）是一間{{link-en|交通网络公司|transportation network company}}，總部位於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[舊金山|舊金山]]，以開發[[流動應用程式|流動應用程式]]連-{}-結乘客和[[司機|司機]]，提供載客車輛[[出租|租賃]]及{{link-en|媒合共乘|Peer-to-peer ridesharing}}的[[分享型經濟|分享型經濟]]服務<ref name="wsj">{{cite news | url=http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2011/06/17/worth-it-an-app-to-get-a-cab/ | title=Worth It? An App to Get a Cab | work=The Wall Street Journal | date=2011-06-17 | agency=Dow Jones & Company | last=Goode | first=Lauren | language=en | accessdate=2014-06-26 | archive-date=2018-08-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826080830/https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2011/06/17/worth-it-an-app-to-get-a-cab/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.uber.com/cities | title=Uber 目前在哪些城市提供服務？ | website=Uber.com | accessdate=2014-08-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526182837/https://www.uber.com/cities | archive-date=2015-05-26 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。乘客可以透過[[應用程式|應用程式]]來預約這些載客的車輛，並且追蹤車輛的位置<ref name="techcrunch.com">{{cite web | url=http://techcrunch.com/2011/09/22/uber-brings-its-disruptive-car-service-to-chicago/ | title=Uber Brings Its Disruptive Car Service To Chicago | publisher=AOL | work=TechCrunch | date=201-09-11 | author=Rao, Leena | language=en | accessdate=2014-06-26 | archive-date=2020-09-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926091723/https://techcrunch.com/2011/09/22/uber-brings-its-disruptive-car-service-to-chicago/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。營運據點分布在全球785個大都市。人們可以透過網站或是手機應用程式進入平台。

優步的名稱大多認為是源自於德文über，和over是同源，意思是「在…上面」。 {{Wayback|url=https://zh.m.wiktionary.org/zh-hant/%C3%BCber |date=20201109040517 }}

然而其營業模式在部分地區面臨法律問題，其非典型的经营模式在部分地區可能會有[[非法營運車輛|非法營運車輛]]的問題，有部分國家或地區已立法將之合法化，例如美国[[加州|加州]]及中國[[北京|北京]]及[[上海|上海]]。原因在於Uber是將計程車行業轉型成社群平台，叫車的客戶透過手機APP（應用程式），就能與欲兼職司機的優步用戶和與有閒置車輛的租戶間三者聯絡，一旦交易成功即按比例抽傭金、分成給予回饋等去監管化的[[金融|金融]]手法。

2019年5月10日，優步公司[[首次公開募股|透過公開發行股票]]成為[[上市公司|上市公司]]，但首日即跌破[[發行價|發行價]]<ref name="xin">{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-05/11/c_1124480382.htm |title=优步上市首日跌破发行价 |accessdate=2019-05-11 |archive-date=2020-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921065007/http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-05/11/c_1124480382.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

據估算，優步在全球有1.1億活跃用戶，在美國有69%的市占率。Uber亦在大中華區開展業務，目前Uber已在[[香港|香港]]和[[台灣|台灣]]建成主流召車服務平台，並於[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]通過换股方式持有該市場最大[[網約車|網約車]]出行平台[[滴滴出行|滴滴出行]]母公司小桔科技17.7%經濟權益<ref>{{cite web|url=https://backlinko.com/uber-users#uber-monthly-active-users|title=Uber Statistics 2021: How Many People Ride with Uber|publisher=BACKLINKO|date=2021-03-23|accessdate=2021-04-21|author=Brain Dean|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421031343/https://backlinko.com/uber-users#uber-monthly-active-users|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
2009年Uber開始在市場出現，最早是在由[[特拉维斯·卡兰尼克|特拉维斯·卡兰尼克]]和[[格瑞特·坎普|格瑞特·坎普]]成立，當時名為「UberCab」。優步在2010年6月正式於舊金山推出服務，同年8月萊恩·格雷夫斯（Ryan Graves）就任執行長。格雷夫斯不久後離開執行長一職，並由卡蘭尼克接任。格雷夫斯目前為營運副總裁和董事會成員<ref name="ceo pumped">{{cite web | url=http://techcrunch.com/2010/12/22/uber-ceo-super-pumped-about-being-replaced-by-founder/ | title=Uber CEO "Super Pumped" About Being Replaced By Founder | publisher=AOL | work=TechCrunch | date=2010-12-22 | author=Arrington, Michael | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2020-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812030058/https://techcrunch.com/2010/12/22/uber-ceo-super-pumped-about-being-replaced-by-founder/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

起初優步學習了倫敦計程車的風格，司機穿著西裝駕駛清一色黑頭的{{link-en|林肯城市轎車|Lincoln Town Cars}}、{{link-en|凱迪拉克凱雷德|Cadillac Escalade}}、[[BMW_7系列|BMW 7系列]]和{{link-en|梅賽德斯-賓士W221|Mercedes-Benz W221|梅賽德斯--{zh-tw:賓士;zh-cn:奔驰;zh-hk:平治; zh-sg:宾士}-S550}}等車系<ref name="techcrunch.com"/>。在2012年後，優步推出「菁英優步」（UberX）服務，加入更多不同系列的車型<ref name="tc20131003">{{cite news | title=In Another Strike Against The Competition, Uber Lowers UberX Prices In San Diego, LA, And DC | url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/10/03/in-another-strike-against-the-competition-uber-lowers-uberx-prices-in-san-diego-la-and-dc/ | accessdate=2013-10-11 | newspaper=Techcrunch | date=2013-10-03 | language=en | archive-date=2020-11-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101023256/https://techcrunch.com/2013/10/03/in-another-strike-against-the-competition-uber-lowers-uberx-prices-in-san-diego-la-and-dc/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。優步在2012年宣布擴展業務計畫，其中包括可搭乘非[[計程車|計程車]]車輛的[[共乘|共乘]]服務<ref name="blog.uber.com">{{cite web | url=http://blog.uber.com/2013/01/31/california-clears-uber-to-continue-and-expand-operations/ | title=California Clears Uber to Continue and Expand Operations | publisher=Uber Blog | date=2013-01-31 | author=Ilya | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2015-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411063839/http://blog.uber.com/2013/01/31/california-clears-uber-to-continue-and-expand-operations/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="techcrunch.com 2">{{cite web | url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/12/uber-ride-sharing/ | title=Look Out, Lyft: Uber CEO Travis Kalanick Says It Will Do Ride Sharing, Too | publisher=AOL | work=TechCrunch | date=2012-09-12 | author=Lawler, Ryan | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813210336/https://techcrunch.com/2012/09/12/uber-ride-sharing/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

優步的行動應用程式在2010年於太平洋地區推出，支援[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]系統的智慧型手機<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2010/11/hailing-a-cab-with-your-phone/66630/ | title=Hailing a Cab With Your Phone | work=The Atlantic | date=2010-11-16 | agency=The Atlantic Monthly Group | last=Jackson | first=Nicholas | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2020-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304165346/https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2010/11/hailing-a-cab-with-your-phone/66630/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年7月24日，優步推出支援[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]的智慧型手機應用程式<ref name="Engadget140724">{{cite web | url=http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/07/23/uber-windows-phone/ | title=Uber 終於為 Windows Phone 推出一個真正的 App | website=Engadget | last=So | first=Marco | date=2014-07-24 | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2017-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614091434/http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/07/23/uber-windows-phone/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年下半，優步獲得加州[[矽谷|矽谷]]一群[[天使投资者|超級天使投資者]]的[[創業投資|創業投資]]資金挹注<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/10/16/idUS353559469920101016 | title=UberCab raises $1.25M to end your futile search for taxis | work=VentureBeat | date=2010-10-16 | agency=Reuters | last=Ha | first=Anthony | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924150146/http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/10/16/idUS353559469920101016 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年初，優步獲得來自創投公司[[Benchmark_(創投公司)|Benchmark]]的3,200萬美元資金<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.launch.is/blog/exclusive-uber-ceo-lays-out-road-map-helicopters-motorcycles.html | title=Exclusive: Uber CEO Lays out Road Map--Helicopters, Motorcycles and Food Delivery | publisher=LAUNCH Media | work=LAUNCH | date=2011-08-16 | language=en | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130180529/http://www.launch.is/blog/exclusive-uber-ceo-lays-out-road-map-helicopters-motorcycles.html | archivedate=2012-01-30 | accessdate=2014-08-14 }}</ref>。2011年下半，優步再次從多位投資者處獲得了3,200萬美元的資金，投資者包括[[高盛|高盛]]、[[Menlo_Ventures|Menlo Ventures]]和[[傑佛瑞·貝佐斯|傑佛瑞·貝佐斯]]等<ref name="cnet.com">{{cite news | url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-57338236-264/car-service-uber-raises-$32-million-launches-in-paris/ | title=Car service Uber raises $32 million, launches in Paris | work=CNET News | date=2011-12-07 | author=Shankland, Stephen | agency=CBS Interactive | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2012-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126193622/http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-57338236-264/car-service-uber-raises-$32-million-launches-in-paris/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，這讓優步獲得的總創投資金達到4,950萬美元。

2012年4月，優步在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]測試以較低價預約傳統計程車的服務<ref>{{cite web | url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/04/18/uber-experiments-with-lower-priced-taxis-in-chicago-through-newly-launched-labs-group-garage/ | script-title=en:Uber Experiments With Lower-Priced Taxis In Chicago Through Newly Launched Labs Group, ‘Garage’ | website=TechCrunch | date=2012-04-18 | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2020-09-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929080520/https://techcrunch.com/2012/04/18/uber-experiments-with-lower-priced-taxis-in-chicago-through-newly-launched-labs-group-garage/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。並於7月進入倫敦市場，最初車隊擁有90位[[賓士|賓士]]、[[BMW|BMW]]和[[捷豹|捷豹]]汽車的駕駛<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/appsblog/2012/jul/02/apps-rush-uber-google-analytics | title=Apps Rush: Uber, Google Analytics... | date=2012-07-02 | agency=The Guardian | author=Dredge, Stuart | location=London | language=en | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2013-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419081257/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/appsblog/2012/jul/02/apps-rush-uber-google-analytics | dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月13日，為慶祝「[[國家冰淇淋月|國家冰淇淋月]]」（National Ice Cream Month），優步在七個城市推出「優步冰淇淋」（Uber Ice Cream）活動。使用者可使用手機應用程式招呼[[冰淇淋車|冰淇淋車]]提供冰淇淋的外送服務，並從使用者的帳戶扣款<ref name="pcmag-icecream">{{cite news|last=Albanesius|first=Chloe|title=Uber Rolling Out On-Demand Ice Cream Trucks|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2407069,00.asp|publisher=PC Magazine|accessdate=2012-08-14|language=en|archive-date=2018-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829110422/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2407069,00.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月3日起，優步開始在[[紐約市|紐約市]]和[[漢普頓|漢普頓]]（The Hamptons）間提供實驗性的直升機招呼服務，稱為「UberCHOPPER」，定價為3,000[[美元|美元]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/uber-helicopter-rides-from-nyc-2013-7 |title=Uber Helicopter Rides From NYC |publisher=Business Insider |date=2013-07-02 |accessdate=2014-01-24 |archive-date=2020-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501141526/https://www.businessinsider.com/uber-helicopter-rides-from-nyc-2013-7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

兩岸三地部分，最起初是於2013年6月27日，優步在[[台灣|台灣]][[台北市|台北市]]試行營運<ref>{{cite web | url=http://blog.uber.com/2013/06/27/ubertaipeisoftlaunch/ | title=UBER 已悄悄地抵達台北囉！ | last=Lo | first=Candice | website=Uber Blog Taipei | publisher=Uber | date=2013-06-27 | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2014-11-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141122095808/http://blog.uber.com/2013/06/27/ubertaipeisoftlaunch/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。並於一個月後在7月31日開始正式營運<ref name="auto">{{cite web | url=http://blog.uber.com/2013/07/31/taipeilaunches/ | title=UBER 正式進軍台北了！ | last=Lo | first=Candice | website=Uber Blog Taipei | publisher=Uber | date=2013-07-31 | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2014-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141123112521/http://blog.uber.com/2013/07/31/taipeilaunches/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2014年3月12日，Uber在上海召开官方发-{}-布会，宣布正式进入中国大陆市场，确定中文名“优-{}-步”，并与[[支付宝|支付宝]]合作。<ref>[http://tech.qq.com/a/20140213/016321.htm Uber入华取名“优步” 拓展沪广深后即将北上] {{Wayback|url=http://tech.qq.com/a/20140213/016321.htm |date=20170913034857 }}. [[腾讯网|腾讯科技]]. 2014-02-13.</ref>經過數個月的試營運後，於同年6月19日正式於[[香港|香港]]部分地區推出服務，初期服務範圍僅涵蓋中環及鄰近地區<ref name="Engadget140619">{{cite web | url=http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/06/19/uber-hong-kong/ | title=Uber 也在香港開動囉！ | website=Engadget | last=So | first=Marco | date=2014-06-19 | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2017-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614085032/http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/06/19/uber-hong-kong/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>；同年8月14日，增加招呼普通計程車的服務<ref name="Engadget140813">{{cite web | url=http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/08/13/uber-taxi-hong-kong/ | title=Uber 香港 Uber 加入普通的士服務！ | website=Engadget | last=So | first=Marco | date=2014-08-14 | accessdate=2014-08-14 | archive-date=2017-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614103449/http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/08/13/uber-taxi-hong-kong/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在中國大陸，人民優步（People's UBER）是優步公司所推出的一個非盈利的公益拼車平台<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Souy