2018年8月8日，紐約市議會決議發布「未來一年內，暫停核發共享計程車的牌照」。此舉將對推行「共享計程車」營運的公司產生嚴重打擊<ref>[https://www.reuters.com/article/us-uber-new-york/new-york-city-votes-to-cap-uber-lyft-vehicle-licenses-idUSKBN1KT2M3 New York City votes to cap Uber, Lyft vehicle licenses] {{Wayback|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-uber-new-york/new-york-city-votes-to-cap-uber-lyft-vehicle-licenses-idUSKBN1KT2M3 |date=20201109033235 }}BUSINESS NEWS 2018-08-09</ref><ref>[https://info.taiwantrade.com/biznews/%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B8%82%E5%B0%87%E5%81%9C%E7%99%BC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E8%A8%88%E7%A8%8B%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-uber-%E5%84%AA%E6%AD%A5-%E5%8F%8Alyft%E5%8F%97%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A-1512742.html?utm_source=newsletter-info&utm_medium=TT-mail&utm_campaign=newsletter-info-20180814-1770&utm_content=biznews-1512742 紐約市將停發共享計程車牌照一年，UBER(優步)及LYFT受打擊] {{Wayback|url=https://info.taiwantrade.com/biznews/%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B8%82%E5%B0%87%E5%81%9C%E7%99%BC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E8%A8%88%E7%A8%8B%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-uber-%E5%84%AA%E6%AD%A5-%E5%8F%8Alyft%E5%8F%97%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A-1512742.html?utm_source=newsletter-info&utm_medium=TT-mail&utm_campaign=newsletter-info-20180814-1770&utm_content=biznews-1512742 |date=20200820114306 }}臺灣經貿網 2018-08-11</ref>。

===== 西雅圖 =====
2014年3月7日，[[西雅圖市議會|西雅圖市議會]]投票通過一項決議，將限制優步、Lyft、SideCar等共乘服務的駕駛人數，標準為每項服務不得超過150人<ref>{{cite news|url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/03/17/seattle-hates-ride-sharing/|title=Seattle Deals A Blow To Uber And Lyft By Limiting The Number Of Ride-Sharing Drivers On The Road|3=|publisher=TechCrunch|date=2014-03-17|accessdate=2014-04-19|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208021943/https://techcrunch.com/2014/03/17/seattle-hates-ride-sharing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。市議會議員[[夏瑪·沙旺特|夏瑪·沙旺特]]（Kshama Sawant）支持這項決議，認為這將可保護傳統的計程車司機<ref>{{cite web|title=Seattle City Council votes to limit number of rideshare drivers on road at one time|url=http://mynorthwest.com/11/2467959/Seattle-City-Council-votes-to-limit-number-of-rideshare-drivers-on-road-at-one-time|publisher=MyNorthwest.com|accessdate=2014-04-19|date=2014-02-27|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314015909/http://mynorthwest.com/11/2467959/Seattle-City-Council-votes-to-limit-number-of-rideshare-drivers-on-road-at-one-time|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，在2014年4月17日，在收到36,000份要求將此議題付諸公投的連署書後，市議會的這項決定被暫時停止執行。市長[[艾德·莫瑞|艾德·莫瑞]]（Ed Murray）宣布將進行為期45天的協商以尋求其他的解決之道<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.geekwire.com/2014/ride-sharing-petition-seattle/|title=Seattle ride-sharing regulations suspended; Mayor wants to negotiate with stakeholders|publisher=GeekWire|date=2014-04-17|accessdate=2014-04-19|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111210903/https://www.geekwire.com/2014/ride-sharing-petition-seattle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2014年7月14日，優步已捐獻超過50萬美元給「西雅圖市民反對124441號命令」（Seattle Citizens to Repeal Ordinance 124441），該團體是一個希望能推翻市議會限制共乘駕駛數量命令的政治團體<ref>{{cite web|title=Contributions to Seattle Citizens to Repeal Ordinance 124441 2014 Election Cycle|url=http://web6.seattle.gov/ethics/elections/poplist.aspx?cid=374&listtype=contributors|website=Seattle.gov|publisher=Seattle Ethics and Elections Commission|accessdate=2014-08-14|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924191750/http://web6.seattle.gov/ethics/elections/poplist.aspx?cid=374&listtype=contributors|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

